Doolan
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Roman Catholic; A Catholic, esp. an Irish Catholic (occas. Irishman); see also Micky Doolan.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
